  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "This page is to understand the Orin Y Power sequence and the relevant code"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The orin_pwrmgr module is a component that runs on the AURIX TC3xx MCU and is responsible for managing the power lifecycle of an NVIDIA Orin SoC."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "In plain terms: the MCU acts as a \"supervisor\" for the Orin SoC -- it controls power rails, monitors voltages and temperatures, handles safe boot chain selection, manages IST (In-System Test) execution, and processes critical failure reports from the SoC via SPI/Etherne"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Architecture Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The module is composed of 4 major composites plus supporting layers:"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "headers": [],
      "rows": [
        [
          "MCU_RefSwModules",
          "Reference (reusable) SW: Platform Power Manager orchestration, I2C driver, Safety Monitor HW abstraction, IST Manager interfaces, Communication coordinator, Common interface"
        ],
        [
          "NvMCU_SwModules",
          "NVIDIA-MCU domain SW: Orin power control (VRS-10/11 regulators), voltage monitoring (VMON), temperature monitoring (TMON), IST Manager core, boot chain configuration, FOH (Fail Operational Handler), config/error codes"
        ],
        [
          "MCU_PlaceHolder",
          "Placeholder/adapter SW: Centralized error handler, Chain-C processing, debug shell"
        ],
        [
          "MCU_NvStubs",
          "NV stubs for NVM Info and Shell interfaces"
        ],
        [
          "rte",
          "Custom RTE layer bridging all composites via FIFO-based error notification, power request/state signaling, IST status sharing, UDP data exchange"
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "MCU_RefSwModules -- Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "MCU_RefSwModules is the reusable reference software layer within orin_pwrmgr . It contains 9 modules that provide hardware abstraction, communication infrastructure, and coordination logi"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/4.0%20Taiji%20AI%20Box%20-%20Orin%20Y%20Power%20Management/image-2026-4-27_13-5-15.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/4.0 Taiji AI Box - Orin Y Power Management/image-2026-4-27_13-5-15.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "OrinY Power sequence"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The power-up is driven by the pPltfPwrMgr_PwrUpOrinStJumpTable in SW_PltfPwrMgr.c . It consists of 14 sequential states executed cyclically from MCU_PltfPwrMgr_SW_RE_Cyclic"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/4.0%20Taiji%20AI%20Box%20-%20Orin%20Y%20Power%20Management/image-2026-4-29_13-48-16.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/4.0 Taiji AI Box - Orin Y Power Management/image-2026-4-29_13-48-16.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Step 0: MCU_PLTFPWRMGR_PWRUP_ORIN_TRIG -- Pre-PowerUp"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "lOrinPwrCtrl_PrePwrUp"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "headers": [
        "Pin",
        "Direction",
        "Action",
        "Purpose"
      ],
      "rows": [
        [
          "SOC_RESET",
          "OUT",
          "Set HIGH",
          "Hold Orin in reset (active-low reset, inverted on P3710+)"
        ],
        [
          "SOC_IST_REQ",
          "OUT",
          "Set LOW",
          "De-assert IST request"
        ],
        [
          "SOC_WAKE",
          "OUT",
          "Set LOW",
          "De-assert wake signal"
        ],
        [
          "SOC_SEQ_VMON_EN",
          "OUT",
          "Set LOW",
          "Disable VRS10 sequencer/VMON"
        ],
        [
          "SOC_SEQ_VMON_SLP",
          "OUT",
          "Set HIGH",
          "Put VRS10 in sleep mode"
        ],
        [
          "SOC_FORCE_RECOVERY",
          "OUT",
          "Set HIGH",
          "De-assert force recovery (active-low)"
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Step 1: MCU_PLTFPWRMGR_ENA_EXT_PWR -- Enable Pre-Regulator"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "lPltfPwrMgr_EnablePREREG"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "headers": [
        "Pin",
        "Direction",
        "Action",
        "Purpose"
      ],
      "rows": [
        [
          "VRS11_U5V0S_ON",
          "OUT",
          "Set HIGH",
          "Enable 5V switched supply rail"
        ],
        [
          "(delay 500us)",
          "--",
          "wait",
          "Settling time"
        ],
        [
          "U15V5S_PRE_ON",
          "OUT",
          "Set HIGH",
          "Enable 15.5V pre-regulator"
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Wait: Polls for Power-Good (PG) with MCU_PLTFPWRMGR_PREREG_PG_WAIT_TIME time"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Step 2: MCU_PLTFPWRMGR_PWRUP_ORIN_CONDTION_CHECK -- Pre-condition Check"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "lPltfPwrMgr_Hndl_PwrUpOrinCondCheck"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "headers": [
        "Pin",
        "Direction",
        "Action",
        "Purpose"
      ],
      "rows": [
        [
          "(ADC check)",
          "IN",
          "Read",
          "Check pre-regulator voltage levels are within range"
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Wait: Debounced check with MCU_PLTFPWRMGR_ORIN_POWERUP_COND_PASS_DEB_TIME using Time_GetEcuTimeMs timestamps. Also has a timeout MCU_PLTFPWRMGR_ORIN_POWERUP_CHECK_TIMEOUT"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Step 3: MCU_PLTFPWRMGR_TRIG_IST -- Trigger IST"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "lPltfPwrMgr_Hndl_TrigIST"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Configures IST Manager for this boot. No direct GPIO -- sets IST parameters via RTE."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Step 4: MCU_PLTFPWRMGR_INIT_TMON -- Initialize Temperature Monitor"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "lPltfPwrMgr_Hndl_InitTMON"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Initializes the Orin TMON sensor over I2C (TMP451). No direct GPIO pin toggle."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Step 5: MCU_PLTFPWRMGR_INIT_VMON -- Initialize Voltage Monitor"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "lPltfPwrMgr_Hndl_InitVMON"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Initializes voltage monitoring (VRS10/VRS11) over I2C. No direct GPIO toggle"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Step 6: MCU_PLTFPWRMGR_PROGRAM_VMON -- Program VMON Thresholds"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "lPltfPwrMgr_Hndl_ProgramVMON"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Programs OV/UV thresholds on VRS10/VRS11 PMIC via I2C. No direct GPIO toggle."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Step 7: MCU_PLTFPWRMGR_PWRUP_VRS10 -- Power-Up VRS10 (Main Orin Supply)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "lPltfPwrMgr_Hndl_PwrUpVRS10"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "headers": [
        "Pin",
        "Direction",
        "Action",
        "Purpose"
      ],
      "rows": [
        [
          "VRS10_VRS11_NIRQ",
          "IN",
          "Read - expect HIGH",
          "Verify no pre-existing faults on VMON"
        ],
        [
          "(I2C)",
          "--",
          "VRS10_Init, VRS11_Init",
          "Configure VRS10/VRS11 PMIC registers"
        ],
        [
          "(I2C)",
          "--",
          "VRS10_Enable",
          "Enable VRS10 power output"
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Wait (RUNNING phase): Polls for NVMCU_ORINPWRCTRL_VRS10_PG_WAIT_TIME , then verifies"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "headers": [
        "Pin / Signal",
        "Direction",
        "Expected",
        "Purpose"
      ],
      "rows": [
        [
          "VRS10_VRS11_NIRQ",
          "IN",
          "HIGH",
          "No fault interrupt from PMIC"
        ],
        [
          "LCVR_PG_ADC",
          "IN (ADC)",
          "HIGH (voltage OK)",
          "LCVR Power-Good"
        ],
        [
          "LCVR_FSI_PG_ADC",
          "IN (ADC)",
          "HIGH (voltage OK)",
          "FSI Power-Good"
        ],
        [
          "LCVR_AO_PG_ADC",
          "IN (ADC)",
          "HIGH (voltage OK)",
          "AO Power-Good"
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "On success, enables FUNC_NIRQ continuous monitoring"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Step 8: MCU_PLTFPWRMGR_VERIFY_PWRUP_VMON -- Verify Power-Up Sequence"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "lPltfPwrMgr_Hndl_VerifyPwrUpSeq"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Verifies all VMON rails are stable after VRS10 power-up. Reads voltage monitoring status."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Step 9: MCU_PLTFPWRMGR_XFI_SOPT -- XFI SOPT Test"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Handler: lPltfPwrMgr_Hndl_XfiSopt (line 2865)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Currently bypassed ( PWRSEQ_BYPASS ). Immediately advances."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Step 10: MCU_PLTFPWRMGR_BOOTCHAIN_SEL -- Boot Chain Selection"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "lPltfPwrMgr_Hndl_BootChain_Sel"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "headers": [
        "Pin",
        "Direction",
        "Action",
        "Purpose"
      ],
      "rows": [
        [
          "SOC_BOOTCHAIN_0",
          "OUT",
          "HIGH or LOW",
          "Boot chain bit 0 (selects A/B/C/D chain)"
        ],
        [
          "SOC_BOOTCHAIN_1",
          "OUT",
          "HIGH or LOW",
          "Boot chain bit 1"
        ],
        [
          "SOC_IST_REQ",
          "OUT",
          "HIGH (if IST boot)",
          "Signal IST boot to Orin"
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Step 11: MCU_PLTFPWRMGR_SETPRERSTCOND -- Set Pre-Reset Conditions"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Handler: lPltfPwrMgr_Hndl_SetPreResetCond Delegates to: NvMCU_OrinPwrCtrl via NVMCU_ORINPWRCTRL_REQ_SETPRERESETCOND Impl: lOrinPwrCtrl_SetPreRstCond"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "headers": [
        "Pin",
        "Direction",
        "Action",
        "Purpose"
      ],
      "rows": [
        [
          "SOC_FORCE_RECOVERY",
          "OUT",
          "HIGH or LOW",
          "Set recovery mode if requested (active-low)"
        ],
        [
          "SOC_XFI_REFCLK_EN",
          "OUT",
          "Set HIGH",
          "Enable XFI Ethernet reference clock to Orin"
        ],
        [
          "(I2C)",
          "--",
          "VRS10_ClearFrcAct",
          "Clear VRS10 Force-Active bit (allow sleep transitions)"
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Step 12: MCU_PLTFPWRMGR_RLS_RST_TEGRA -- Release Orin Reset"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Handler: lPltfPwrMgr_Hndl_RlsRstTegra Delegates to: NvMCU_OrinPwrCtrl via NVMCU_ORINPWRCTRL_REQ_REL_RESET Impl: lOrinPwrCtrl_RlsRst"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "headers": [
        "Pin",
        "Direction",
        "Action",
        "Purpose"
      ],
      "rows": [
        [
          "SOC_RESET",
          "OUT",
          "Set LOW",
          "Release Orin from reset (active-low, inverted) -- Orin starts booting"
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Post-reset actions (same handler):"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "Enables Orin TMON thermal monitoring",
        "Enables VRS11 PG monitoring (if not in recovery mode)",
        "Starts FOH (First Orin Heartbeat) monitoring with delay"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Step 13: MCU_PLTFPWRMGR_PWRUP_ORIN_SEQ_COMPLETE -- Sequence Complete"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Handler: lPltfPwrMgr_Hndl_PwrUpOrinSeqEnd (line 3793)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Transitions state to MCU_PLTFPWRMGR_PWRUP_ORIN_FINISH . Orin is now booting."
    }
  ],
